# Push Notification vs In-App Notification

### Push Notification

Appears on the phone even when the app is closed.

Example:

```text
📄 Time to upload your latest blood report.
```

---

### In-App Notification

Only appears after opening the app.

Example:

```text
Welcome back!

You uploaded your last report 7 months ago.

Ready to upload your latest report?
```

For the MVP, support both.

---

# Notification History

Users should also be able to view past notifications.

Example:

```text
Notification Center

15 Jan

Upload Reminder

----------------

10 Jul

AI Summary Ready

----------------

05 Jan

Welcome
```

---

# Respect User Privacy

Never include detailed health information in a push notification.

Good:

```text
Your report summary is ready.
```

Bad:

```text
Your HbA1c is high.
```

---

